# Flycast Project Context

**What it is:** Real-time announcement board for live demo at Cursor Meetup Split (March 3, 2026). Admin writes or dictates messages; audience sees them instantly via QR code.

**Tech stack:** Next.js 16 (App Router), TypeScript strict, Supabase (Notical project), Tailwind v4, Web Speech API.

**Out of scope (MVP):** Message categories, delete, expiry, push notifications, dark mode, Supabase auth, AI features beyond speech-to-text. Do not add these unless explicitly requested.

**Spec reference:** Full technical spec at `~/Desktop/flycast-technical-spec.md` — consult for detailed behavior, routes, and schema.
